OL,3,CThe best and worst NHS trusts for
OL,4,Ccancer treatment targets
OL,6,FAlmost all NHS trusts in England are
OL,7,Fmissing a major cancer target ` with
OL,8,Fsome of the worst performers treating
OL,9,Fonly half of patients within a target
OL,10,Ftime period, new data shows.
OL,12,FNew figures reveal stark differences
OL,13,Fin cancer waiting times across the
OL,14,Fcountry, with some patients waiting
OL,15,Fmore than 104 days to begin treatment.
OL,17,FThe NHS has a longstanding target for
OL,18,F85% of patients to start treatment
OL,19,Fwithin 62 days of an urgent cancer
OL,20,Freferral.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
