OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1772055663
OL,3,CThe best and worst NHS trusts for
OL,4,Ccancer treatment targets
OL,6,FThat target has not been met
OL,7,Fnationally since 2014.
OL,9,FAn analysis of NHS England data by the
OL,10,FPress Association shows just three of
OL,11,F119 acute trusts with comparable data
OL,12,Fhit or surpassed the 85% target last
OL,13,Fyear.
OL,15,FAround a quarter reached the
OL,16,Fgovernment's interim target of 75%,
OL,17,Fwhich it has set as a milestone for
OL,18,FMarch 2026.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
