OL,3,CThe best and worst NHS trusts for
OL,4,Ccancer treatment targets
OL,6,FThe three trusts meeting the 85%
OL,7,Fstandard were Calderdale and
OL,8,FHuddersfield (89.2%), Home
OL,10,Frton Healthcare (85.8%) and Maidstone
OL,11,Fand Tunbridge Wells (85.7%).
OL,13,FHere are the best and worst performing
OL,14,Ftrusts, according to the latest
OL,15,Fanalysis:
OL,17,FFigures show the percentage of
OL,18,Fpatients who began cancer treatment
OL,19,Fwithin 62 days of an urgent referral
OL,20,Fin 2025, with the 2024 figure in
OL,21,Fbrackets.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
