OL,3,CThe best and worst NHS trusts for
OL,4,Ccancer treatment targets
OL,6,FTop five trusts:
OL,8,FBottom five trusts:
OL,10,FAcross England, 69.1% of patients -
OL,11,F239,038 out of 345,847 - began cancer
OL,12,Ftreatment within 62 days last year, up
OL,13,Fslightly from 67.7% in 2024, but well
OL,14,Fbelow the 85% target.
OL,16,FSome 65 of the 119 trusts improved
OL,17,Ftheir performance year on year, while
OL,18,F54 saw a fall.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
