OL,3,CThe best and worst NHS trusts for
OL,4,Ccancer treatment targets
OL,6,FFour trusts met the 85% standard in
OL,7,F2024, compared with three in 2025,
OL,8,Fwith Calderdale and Huddersfield
OL,9,Ftopping the list in both years.
OL,11,FAn NHS spokesman said: "The NHS is
OL,12,Fseeing and treating record numbers of
OL,13,Fpatients for cancer, with more than
OL,14,Fthree quarters of people receiving a
OL,15,Fdiagnosis or all clear within four
OL,16,Fweeks, but there are still too many
OL,17,Fpeople experiencing unacceptably long
OL,18,Fwaits for their first treatment.
