OL,3,CThe best and worst NHS trusts for
OL,4,Ccancer treatment targets
OL,6,F"Our landmark National Cancer Plan
OL,7,Fsets out a clear roadmap to ensuring
OL,8,Fwe are meeting all three cancer
OL,9,Fstandards to see and treat patients on
OL,10,Ftime over the next three years, with
OL,11,Ffurther improvements to make care more
OL,12,Fpersonalised and significantly improve
OL,13,Fsurvival."
OL,15,FIn a handful of trusts, at least one
OL,16,Fin seven patients who began cancer
OL,17,Ftreatment in December 2025 had waited
OL,18,Fmore than 104 days since their urgent
OL,19,Freferral, other PA analysis shows.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@JO]
