OL,3,CThe best and worst NHS trusts for
OL,4,Ccancer treatment targets
OL,6,FAt University Hospitals of Leicester,
OL,7,F13.7% of patients starting treatment
OL,8,Fthat month had waited this long,
OL,9,Frising to 14.5% at Queen Elizabeth
OL,10,FHospital King's Lynn, 14.9% at
OL,11,FSheffield Teaching Hospitals and 15.5%
OL,12,Fat Guy's and St Thomas'.
OL,14,FThe proportion reached one in six at
OL,15,FHull University Teaching Hospitals
OL,16,F(16.5%) and Mid and South Essex
OL,17,F(17.0%).
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
