OL,3,CThe best and worst NHS trusts for
OL,4,Ccancer treatment targets
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FMichelle Mitchell, chief executive of
OL,12,FCancer Research UK, said: "Every
OL,13,Fcancer patient deserves access to
OL,14,Ftimely, high-quality care.
OL,16,F"Although NHS staff are working hard
OL,17,Fto cope with increasing pressure on
OL,18,Fcancer services, far too many people
OL,19,Fstill face unacceptable delays for
OL,20,Fvital treatment.
